    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapists just try to fix things that are already gone. they talk about \"healing\" like there's some version of me left to repair. but there isn't. the essence of who i was is just... erased. it's like trying to fix a house after it's been burned to the ground. you're just staring at the ashes.",
